{"tid":402161,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線，依家D小朋友由細細個已經開始吸毒","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T07:17:06.000Z","uid":5713,"like":664,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b03a6871cdf863c9544bb342b0432da3f281d1","tid":402161,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"係吉野家食緊窮撚下午茶 隔離幾台有個老豆同佢個仔 （6-8歲左右）<br />\n佢個仔喊撚哂口話要睇手機 佢老豆就話手機無電無得睇<br />\n之後佢喊到拆天咁 成間鋪既人都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n呢個時候佢老豆個朋友買完野食番黎 話比部手機佢睇卡通片 佢死都唔要 係要佢老豆果部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔會比小朋友咁細個就睇手機 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇咪睇lo 唔好撚煩到我就得"},{"pid":"92ac839e1813ca69cfcede0f92b47fd4db32af97","tid":402161,"uid":5713,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"屌 依家個老豆抱住佢走 同佢個fd 講話上去拎尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢個fd 一個人睇住三個餐 個樣好老懢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d39f3211cf2d7576081f6b0c4dee1af4df02b8","tid":402161,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3342b880362b19cab54acc6c3b03887079d9431","tid":402161,"uid":51518,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"始終科技先進左，好難完全唔俾佢地玩，不過會盡量限住佢用囉，我個囡三歲幾，每次都係部電話較十分鐘鬧鐘，響就俾返我，咁起碼隔一段時間先再用。"},{"pid":"e0f8cbc32a08ba429089d466473d4a6fee8ed3f4","tid":402161,"uid":5713,"like":10